<h2 id="publishing-your-exocore">Publishing Your Exocore</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Make a Netlify account</li>
  <li>Connect it to your Newly forked repo</li>
  <li>Push your Exocore to Github to publish as a website</li>
</ol>

