<h3 id="appendix-using-git-for-the-first-time">Appendix: Using Git for the first time</h3>
<p>Git is a version management software which allows you to synchronise a project in multiple places at once. For the purposes of the Exocore, it is a way to edit your project locally, and push it to the web to be deployed as a website.</p>

